{"tid":1448313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明天1PM全民入機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:14.000Z","uid":300622,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ba9de89a8e33bb4183d6115918efefb46011c6","tid":1448313,"uid":300622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvPzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=f79fe7c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvPzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=2ca40a85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"f1dc1012b8de9928acccc47d50b0b84968173951","tid":1448313,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仲唔孝敬班警察屋企人仲等乜呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446089</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"779fe240f0e7670689e825dc8585acf8a284cb64","tid":1448313,"uid":30982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79b86da537d1c92bebf3fb1b91e26027296ac750","tid":1448313,"uid":282600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c10a8c1070e00588c7ce68a1098e34898c218b3","tid":1448313,"uid":83106,"like